  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2060770">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2060770/" class="title-link">希特勒的读书生活</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2060770"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tensor/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1065130-33.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tensor/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">无机客</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-06-06"
      class="main-meta">2009-06-06 21:45:08</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2060770_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  据资料记载，希特勒的私人藏书室共有大约16000册藏书，分别位于柏林、慕尼黑和德国东南部的贝希特斯加登三地。其中，藏于柏林的帝国总理宅邸的约万册图书，在苏联红军攻占柏林后，被苏联方面运至柏林。在上世纪九十年代，有传言说该批书籍在莫斯科的一家荒废的教堂中现身，但随...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2060770/#comments">(47回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">129有用 / 6没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            Knopf2008版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2060770_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2060770_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5685617">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5685617/" class="title-link">希特勒读什么书？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5685617"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ygy8245/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1042441-29.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ygy8245/" class="author">
